name: Versamix-Realistic
description:
Decided to split my base model into realistic and anime styles because trying to both will worsen the quality of both styles.

This model focuses on semirealistic to realistic images.

Recommended Parameters

Sampler: DPM++2M Karras, DPM++ SDE Karras, Euler a, DDIM

Sampling Steps: 20-30

CFG: 7-10

Clip: 2

Negative Embeddings: bad_pictures
